# User-filled configs. The .template.json files are the source of truth in
# the repo; brand.json / auth.json / constraints.json are produced per-user
# by `reframe init` (or by Stage 0's bootstrap) and may contain customer
# branding, test logins, or domain-specific rules. Keep them local.
config/brand.json
config/auth.json
config/constraints.json

# Video composition (internal source for the demo gif). The rendered gif
# lives in assets/ and ships with the repo; the source is authoring-only.
video/

